  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1. Add at lease one contact\r\n2. Open the Chat screen > Press the `+` button > `New chat`\r\n3. Select the contact\r\n4. Check is the button is visible at the bottom of the bottom sheet\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nThe `Chat with ...` / `Setup group chat` button is fully visible on any display size\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nThe button is fully visible only on devices with a display larger than 5\"\r\n\r\nExamples:\r\n\r\nGalaxy Nexus 4.65\"\r\n<img width=\"679\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-02-13 at 17 05 56\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/218509707-964ccc82-fa3b-415e-a747-624570b0fdab.png\">\r\n\r\niPhone SE 4.7\"\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/218510531-2b5dcb2d-c5d0-4755-b564-51e442d9e755.MP4\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: rc1\r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
